OL,3,CFlood-ravaged communities on the
OL,4,CEngland-Wales border feel left behind
OL,6,FFlood-ravaged communities along the
OL,7,Fhave slammed a cross-border scheme
OL,8,Fbetween English and Welsh authorities
OL,9,Ffor moving too slowly as water levels
OL,10,Fsurge following heavy rain in the
OL,11,Fregion.
OL,13,FThe Severn Valley Flood Management
OL,14,FScheme involves government agencies
OL,15,Fand councils on both sides of the
OL,16,Fborder, and was launched at the end of
OL,17,F2020.
