OL,4,CEngland-Wales border feel left behind
OL,6,FBut more than three years later, and
OL,7,Fdespite being awarded #10 million in
OL,8,Fgovernment funding, campaigners have
OL,9,Fsaid they've yet to see any progress.
OL,11,FThe latest State of the UK Climate
OL,12,Freport suggests the UK has become
OL,13,Fnoticeably wetter, with the years 2011
OL,14,Fto 2020 seeing 9% more rainfall than
OL,15,Fthe years 1961 to 1990.
OL,17,F"I think there was a recent update on
OL,18,Ftheir website, but then there's been
OL,19,Fvery little in the last year," said
OL,20,FSiobhan Connor, of the Shrewsbury
OL,21,FFlood Action Group.
