OL,6,F"There's a real lack of information. I
OL,7,Fwant to see timelines, when this is
OL,8,Fhappening, what we can expect... I
OL,9,Fthink this is probably 20 years away,
OL,10,Fbut the frequency of flooding is
OL,11,Fgetting higher and higher."
OL,13,FAmong those who are feeling the
OL,14,Feffects are residents in , including
OL,15,FSarah Jackaman, .
OL,17,FAfter a winter of severe floods,
OL,18,FSarah's house in Shrewsbury is still
OL,19,Fdrying out, and the especially cold
OL,20,Fweather has meant that it has taken
OL,21,Flonger than usual.
