OL,4,CEngland-Wales border feel left behind
OL,6,FSarah does everything she can and
OL,7,Fspends thousands of pounds of her own
OL,8,Fmoney to put flood barriers up.
OL,10,FShe's become accustomed to moving her
OL,11,Ffurniture upstairs, or onto stilts -
OL,12,Fhas had to make huge changes to the
OL,13,Fbuilding itself to help keep it as
OL,14,Fresilient as possible.
OL,16,FBut there's no way to stop the water
OL,17,Fgetting in.
OL,19,F"The water level through the house
OL,20,Freaches just above the ankle level,"
OL,21,Fshe said.
