OL,6,F"The flooring has been relaid, so
OL,7,Fwe've put terracotta ceramic tiles
OL,8,Fdown.
OL,10,F"We've put flood barriers on the
OL,11,Fdoors. And we've actually changed the
OL,12,Fpaint and the plaster that we use, so
OL,13,Fthat it's more resilient to the
OL,14,Fflooding.
OL,16,F"It makes the clean-up much easier
OL,17,Fafterwards too."
