OL,4,CEngland-Wales border feel left behind
OL,6,FEd Tate runs the Isle Farm, which is
OL,7,Fsurrounded by a loop of the Severn,
OL,8,Fmeaning he has to find ways to survive
OL,9,Fwith regular flooding.
OL,11,FEach time the water rises and his land
OL,12,Ffloods, it costs him around #10,000 in
OL,13,Fclean up costs, while wheat yields are
OL,14,Fexpected to be around 20% lower this
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FHe estimates challenges like this risk
OL,18,Faround 40% of small and medium-sized
OL,19,Ffarms across the UK.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/15
