OL,4,CEngland-Wales border feel left behind
OL,6,FHe said: "We're all in this together,
OL,7,Fwhether you're a householder or a
OL,8,Fbusiness. We've got climate change,
OL,9,Fwe've got biodiversity loss, we've got
OL,10,Ffood and water security challenges,"
OL,11,Fhe said.
OL,13,F"As farmers, as land managers, we're
OL,14,Fvery well positioned to give us food
OL,15,Fsecurity and that environmental
OL,16,Fsecurity. But we need support. It
OL,17,Fcosts money.
