OL,6,F"If we're to address the effects of
OL,7,Fclimate change, we need grown-up
OL,8,Fgovernance - we need to talk across
OL,9,Fborders.
OL,11,F"We need to work out a way that
OL,12,Ffinancing can cross borders.
OL,14,F"So that, at every point, we can
OL,15,Factually manage water right the way
OL,16,Fdown from source to sea on the Severn."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/15
