OL,6,F"We need to talk about borders. We
OL,7,Fneed to work out a way that financing
OL,8,Fcan cross borders. So at every point
OL,9,Fwe can actually manage water right the
OL,10,Fway down from source to sea on the
OL,11,FSevern."
OL,13,FIn response an Environment Agency
OL,14,Fspokesperson insisted that cross-
OL,15,Fborder thinking was already happening.
