OL,6,F"In recent months, we have formalised
OL,7,Four partnership with Natural Resources
OL,8,FWales, Powys County Council and
OL,9,FShropshire Council to agree a
OL,10,Fstrategic approach to cross-border
OL,11,Fworking, supported by Welsh Government
OL,12,Fand Defra."
OL,14,F"This year, the Severn Valley Water
OL,15,FManagement Scheme and partners will
OL,16,Flaunch a comprehensive programme of
OL,17,Fengagement to further support the
OL,18,Fdevelopment of a long-term Strategy
OL,19,Fand approach, which will help create
OL,20,Fresilient communities and natural
OL,21,Fenvironments across the region."
