OL,6,FA spokesperson for Natural Resources
OL,7,FWales said: "As climate change brings
OL,8,Fmore frequent and more extreme weather
OL,9,Fconditions, the challenges of managing
OL,10,Fwater will increase, and we will need
OL,11,Fto look at a combination of measures
OL,12,Fto manage flood risk.
OL,14,F"This means making big decisions about
OL,15,Fwhere development is allowed, and
OL,16,Fmaking properties more resilient to
OL,17,Fflood water.
