OL,6,F"We'll also need to be more innovative
OL,7,Fand look at harnessing nature-based
OL,8,Fsolutions to flooding and work more
OL,9,Feffectively with landowners, and
OL,10,Ftaking catchment-scale approaches to
OL,11,Fmake space for the huge quantities of
OL,12,Fwater we are seeing during floods."
